+/**
+ * Spanner PostgreSQL specific emulation of array_remove_index.
+ *
+ * Spanner does not support the {@code IS DISTINCT FROM} operator, so this
+ * emulation uses a null-safe inequality check using {@code coalesce}.
+ */
